nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE DEGENERATES TO A REMNANT LOW... ...EXPECTED TO RESTRENGTHEN TO A TROPICAL STORM OVER THE WEEKEND...
summary: ...HENRIETTE DEGENERATES TO A REMNANT LOW... ...EXPECTED TO RESTRENGTHEN TO A TROPICAL STORM OVER THE WEEKEND... As of 11:00 AM HST Fri Aug 08 the center of Henriette was located near 19.9, -143.0 with movement WNW at 17 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1009 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 35 mph.
